- [ ] Selecting items enables BulkActionToolbar with Publish/Unpublish/Archive/Export actions; actions require confirmation and can be undone.
- [ ] ItemDetailDrawer displays complete metadata, provides quick actions to open in the pipeline, and shows pipeline state/runs.
- [ ] Pipeline integration is wired: opening an item shows pipeline state; actions link to the Content Pipeline Automation workflow.
- [ ] API response handling includes robust validation and safe defaults; all endpoints guarded by runtime checks.
- [ ] UI adheres to the provided design system: color palette, typography, spacing, card styling, navigation, and data visualization guidelines.
- [ ] All new code passes TypeScript typings (or project language) and includes unit tests or integration tests where feasible.

